			<title><![CDATA[Atech raises Pre-Seed to unlock a new era of Physical AI builders with the &quot;Lovable for hardware&quot;]]></title>
			<category><![CDATA[Hardware]]></category>
			<link>https://tech.eu/2026/04/27/atech-raises-pre-seed-to-unlock-the-next-wave-of-physical-ai-builders/</link>
